716346f-a.title: ??Manhattan: Amsterdam Avenue - 161st Street (West)
716346f-a.text:
Amsterdam Ave., north from West 161st Street. Note the traffic arrow (in the center) pointing in the direction of St. Nicholas Ave.,which intersects at this point and runs true northward and southward.

August 27, 1936.

W.P.A. Photo.
Federal ARt Project.
Credit Line Imperative on All Reproductions.

715708f-a.text:
517 West 161st Street, north side, between Amsterdam Ave., and Broadway. Building is a frame house.
November 0, 1927.
P.. L. Sperr.
